item.description: Hello, World! My name is, well, Adam Wilson and I'm the National Company Relations Manager @LaunchCode here in beautiful #STL, my hometown. When I'm not speaking with companies, cities, and candidates about LaunchCode, I'm a husband to Anita, father to Eli, son to Quentin and Nancy, brother to Ben, uncle to Eloise, educator, equal-rights advocate, and EdTech Entrepreneur.
